xml:lang="en">These Web maps are overlain with a regular grid of dots (\ufffd\ufffd\ufffddot maps\ufffd\ufffd\ufffd) or grid of cells, where each dot represents a ground station and each cell represents a spatially aggregated geophysical variable.
